<plot>Every May in glittering Las Vegas, the world's best poker players pay up to $10,000 of their own money to compete in the ultimate card game . . . the World Series of Poker. POKER KINGS follows the high stakes journey of five players over 12 months in their quest to win poker's Holy Grail and its $2.5 million first prize. Featuring: Phil Hellmuth, Jr., Simon Trumper, Garry Bush, Rob Varkonyi and Carlo Citrone.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?437319</url></doc>
